        "Judging criteria weights (Innovation, Feasibility, Presentation, etc.)",
        "Mentor availability schedule",
        "Submission platform (DevPost, GitHub, etc.)",
        "Prizes per track",
        "Meals and refreshments plan",
        "Hardware hackathon: equipment/hardware provided"
